<p>
   <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Washington</ENAMEX>, <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Sept. 3</TIMEX> (<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Bloomberg</ENAMEX>) -- The <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">U.S.</ENAMEX> launched a second
missile attack on sites in <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Iraq</ENAMEX>, aiming to finish off targets fired
